Harry could barely breathe: Could luck, sheer luck, get them safely out of
this?
“Well, well.” said Greyback, and Harry could hear the tiniest note of trepidation in that callous voice, and knew that Greyback was wondering whether he
had just indeed just attacked and bound the son of a Ministry Official. Harry’s
